    assertEquals(
        epochAfterMetadataUpdate,
        heartbeatResult.records().stream()
            .filter(r -> r.key() instanceof ConsumerGroupTargetAssignmentEpochKey)
            .map(r -> ((ConsumerGroupTargetAssignmentEpochValue) r.value()).epoch())
            .findFirst()
            .orElse(-1));
}
```

**Coverage Delta**:
- Tests concurrent heartbeat processing and metadata updates
