            .setGroupId(groupId)
            .setMemberId(memberId)
            .setMemberEpoch(1)
            .setRebalanceTimeoutMs(5000)
            .setSubscribedTopicRegex("[invalid"))); // Invalid regex
}
```

**Coverage Delta**:
- Tests regex validation (throwIfRegexInvalid) during mid-rebalance member states
- Validates consistent error prioritization (which error to report first)
- Exercises code path at GroupMetadataManager ~line 2350-2380

